The '''Golden Spoon''', also known as the '''Golden Spatula''', was an award given for exceptional cooking. [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|Jabba the Hutt's]] chef [[Porcellus/Legends|Porcellus]] was awarded the Golden Spoon three times.

==Behind the scenes==
In [[Star Wars Galaxies|''Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided'']], Porcellus called the prize a Golden Spatula, rather than a Golden Spoon. One of the spatulas can be seen hanging in the kitchen.

